• If the email involves enterprise matters such as contracts, subscriptions, legal issues, billing, investor follow-up, or account management, route to 'ben'. 
• If the email concerns external communications like training, webinars, market research, press inquiries, partnerships, or events, route to 'tom'.
Do not include your internal reasoning in the final output. Return exactly a JSON object with a single key 'route_to' and its value set to the appropriate routing target (either ben, jerry, or tom).
